text:
The order you placed has been served.
It's the seasonal tea and scone set──
Please, take your time and enjoy your meal.

Yeah...! Somehow... it was cool!
I'm not sure if 'cool' is the right word though...!

...Yeah, seeing you work so diligently
is really impressive...

Yeah,
let's drink up while it's still warm.

...Mmm, this tea has a lovely aroma.
The scones go really well with the jam and cream...

It seems like the result of
many people doing good work.

...Their careful workmanship...
it feels like it gives us energy somehow...
